                                    <td class="content" rowspan="2" align="left" valign="top" height="340" width="100%">
                                        <!-- Begin Dyamic Content Zone -->
                                        <CENTER><H1>Traveling to UC Irvine</H1></CENTER>
                                                                                
                                        <A HREF="http://www.uci.edu/campusmap/"
                                        TARGET="window"><IMG SRC="images/fwy_map_thumbnail.jpg" WIDTH="116"
                                        HEIGHT="128" ALIGN="RIGHT" HSPACE="25" BORDER="0"></A>
                                        
                                        <UL>
                                        <LI><A HREF="#LA">From Los Angeles</A>
                                        <LI><A HREF="#RS">From Riverside/San Bernardino</A>
                                        <LI><A HREF="#SD">From San Diego</A>
                                        <LI><A HREF="#Park">Parking</A>
                                        <LI><A HREF="#Air">Traveling by Air</A>
                                        <LI><A HREF="#Train">Traveling by Train</A>
                                        <LI><A HREF="#Hotel">Hotel Accommodations</A>
                                        
                                        </UL>
                                        
                                        <A NAME="LA">&nbsp;</A>
                                        <H2>From Los Angeles</H2>
                                        
                                        Take the 405 freeway south to Jamboree Road.  Turn right on Jamboree,
                                        then left at Campus Drive and right at West Peltason Drive to enter the
                                        campus.  UCI is located approximately one hour from Los Angeles.
                                        <BR><BR>
                                        
                                        
                                        <A NAME="RS">&nbsp;</A>
                                        <H2>From Riverside/San Bernardino</H2>
                                        Take the 91 freeway west, to the 55 freeway south, to the 405 freeway
                                        south.  Exit at Jamboree Road and turn right, then left at Campus
                                        Drive and right at West Peltason Drive to enter the campus.  UCI is
                                        located approximately 50 minutes from Riverside.
                                        <BR><BR>
                                        
                                        
                                        <A NAME="SD">&nbsp;</A>
                                        <H2>From San Diego</H2>
                                        Take Interstate 5 north to the 405 freeway.  Exit at Culver and turn
                                        left.  Proceed to Campus Drive and turn right.  Turn left at West
                                        Peltason Drive to enter the campus.  UCI is located approximately
                                        90 minutes from San Diego.
                                        <BR><BR>
                                        
                                        
                                        <A NAME="Park">&nbsp;</A>
                                        <H2>Parking</H2>
                                        Visitors may park in metered space for $1/hour.  
                                        <A HREF="http://www.parking.uci.edu/permits/guestparking.cfm"
                                        TARGET="parking">Daily parking permits</A> 
                                        may be purchased for $7 at the kiosk located at the West 
                                        Peltason Drive entrance, or $6 for half day permits (8a.m.-12 noon or 
                                        12 noon-5p.m.).  Also available are weekly permits for $20.
                                        Parking is limited, so please allow extra time before your appointment or
                                        tour.  It is recommended that you park in the parking structure
                                        directly across from the Student Center, at West Peltason and
                                        Pereira Drives.<P>
                                        
                                        If you plan to be on campus for under two hours, you may elect to park
                                        at the meters in parking lots #1 and #2 (beyond the Administration Building).
                                        You will have to enter the campus from Berkeley Drive/East Peltason
                                        (<A HREF="http://www.uci.edu/campusmap/"
                                        TARGET="window">see map</A>). Meter parking in these lots is $2.00 for
                                        two hours. Payment is made in quarters only.  No change is available.
                                        For more information, contact
                                        <A HREF="http://www.parking.uci.edu/" TARGET="window">Parking and
                                        Transportation Services</A>.
                                        <BR><BR>
                                        
                                        
                                        <A NAME="Air">&nbsp;</A>
                                        <H2>Traveling by Air</H2>
                                        UC Irvine is located just two miles from John Wayne/Orange Country
                                        Airport.  Cab fares run about $10.  To drive to UC Irvine from the
                                        airport, follow the Campus Drive signs out of the airport and take
                                        Campus Drive to West Peltason Drive.  Turn right to enter the
                                        campus.<P>
                                        
                                        Los Angeles International Airport (LAX) is located about 45 miles
                                        north of Irvine.  SuperShuttle fare is about $35 per person from
                                        LAX to UC Irvine.  For more information call (800) 200-6655.
                                        <BR><BR>
                                        
                                        <A NAME="Train">&nbsp;</A>
                                        <H2>Traveling by Train</H2>
                                        Amtrak offers daily north-south service to Irvine.  Cab fares from
                                        the station to campus are about $15.  Contact Amtrak at (800)
                                        872-7245 for further information.
                                        <BR><BR>
                                        
                                        
                                        <A NAME="Hotel">&nbsp;</A>
                                        <H2>Hotel Accommodations</H2>
                                        For information on nearby accommodations, see
                                        <A HREF="http://www.confserv.uci.edu/o_hotel.htm"
                                        TARGET="window">www.confserv.uci.edu/o_hotel.htm</A>.
                                        <BR><BR CLEAR="all">

